.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, january
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike
1. the person drinking cola is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's birthday is in january##2
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | sprite  | cola  | milk        |
| Birthday       | january | july | may |
| Transport   | boat    | car   | quad-bike   |

