1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | martial-arts | action |
| Hobby   | fishing        | rock-climbing         | sudoku |
| Pet           | chinchilla | pony         | frog   |

